<section class="health-benefits">
  <h2>🩺 Health Benefits: Peanut Butter & Jelly Hot Cereal</h2>

  <h3>🧠 Brain & Mood Support</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Wild blueberries + black currants:</strong> Rich in anthocyanins for memory, neuroprotection, and improved mood.</li>
    <li><strong>Flax, chia, and hemp:</strong> Provide ALA omega-3s, essential for brain health and neurotransmitter balance.</li>
    <li><strong>Rosemary:</strong> Shown to support cognitive clarity and long-term brain function.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>💓 Heart & Blood Sugar Regulation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Steel cut oats + buckwheat:</strong> Deliver soluble fiber to lower cholesterol and stabilize blood sugar.</li>
    <li><strong>Peanut butter (no sugar/oil):</strong> Provides healthy fats and protein that slow digestion and reduce glucose spikes.</li>
    <li><strong>Cinnamon:</strong> Known to improve insulin sensitivity and lower fasting glucose in some individuals.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>💩 Gut & Microbiome Health</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Dates, berries, and seeds:</strong> Offer prebiotic fibers that feed beneficial gut bacteria like <em>Bifidobacteria</em> and <em>Akkermansia</em>.</li>
    <li><strong>Chia, flax, and hemp:</strong> Support healthy digestion and gut motility with both soluble and insoluble fiber.</li>
    <li><strong>No emulsifiers, gums, or oils:</strong> Helps protect gut lining and avoid inflammation.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>🏋️‍♀️ Muscle, Bone & Recovery Support</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Complete protein:</strong> Oats, buckwheat, and seeds provide all essential amino acids.</li>
    <li><strong>Magnesium-rich ingredients:</strong> Help prevent cramping and support muscle/nerve recovery.</li>
    <li><strong>Calcium from walnut milk + seeds:</strong> Supports bones and neuromuscular function.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>🌿 Anti-Inflammatory & Antioxidant Power</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Polyphenols:</strong> Found in berries, rosemary, and cinnamon — reduce oxidative stress and inflammation.</li>
    <li><strong>Whole food only:</strong> No added sugars, oils, or flours — helps prevent chronic inflammation triggers.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="summary-box">
    <h4>🛡️ Summary</h4>
    <p>This hot cereal is low glycemic, fiber-rich, high in antioxidants, gut-supportive, protein-complete, and anti-inflammatory — all in one bowl.</p>
  </div>
</section>

